OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Flargely dry through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight but with a few outbreaks of
OL,8,Flight rain at times. Patchy cloud with
OL,9,Fclear spells.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FA mostly dry start with some
OL,12,Fbright spells. Turning cloudier
OL,13,Fthrough the middle of the day before
OL,14,Fbecoming clearer again by evening.
OL,15,FLargely dry, chance of some showers in
OL,16,Fwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
