OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry on Friday, chance of rain for a
OL,7,Ftime in the afternoon. Dry and bright
OL,8,Ffor most of Saturday, some rain later.
OL,9,FVariable cloud but mainly dry Sunday.
